prompts.frontCover:
Front cover of a birthday greeting card for Lao Lao, humorous and lighthearted. A funny, charming cartoon illustration of an elderly Asian woman and a young Asian man, based on the reference photo, in a beautiful watercolor painting style. The characters highly resemble the people in the photo, with the same hairstyles, facial features, body proportions, and clothing (omit any text/logos). The Lao Lao character is playfully and dramatically attempting to lift a very large, comically oversized dumbbell with a strained, funny expression on her face. The young man stands beside her, cheering her on with an encouraging and amused expression, holding a tiny party blower. The background is a soft, minimalist wash of pastel colors with artistic paint splatters and organic bleeds, suggesting a festive but clean setting. Centered in the middle of the card, in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script, is the text: "Happy Birthday, Lao Lao! You're still the strongest!". The entire image is flat 2D, with visible paper texture and artistic watercolor brushstrokes. --ar 5:7 --style raw --v 6.0 --s 250 --cref 10ed1a71-7de4-421e-be3b-05bdfcf78928 --cw 100

- Reference photos provided for character creation
- Characters should only appear on the front cover
- Transform real people into artistic cartoon/illustrated versions matching the style
- Maintain recognizable features while adapting to the artistic style
